        "date": "2026-06-12T13:51:50Z",
        "message": "fix(docs): bump engines.node to >=18.0.0 (matches CI matrix) (#1254)\n\n* fix(docs): bump engines.node to >=18.0.0 (matches CI matrix)\n\nThe package.json advertised node >=14.0.0 but:\n- CI matrix starts at node 18 (.github/workflows/pull-request.yml)\n- @types/node devDep is ^18.0.0\n- Package is ESM-only ('type': 'module'); Node 14 had ESM behind a flag\n\nBumping engines.node to >=18.0.0 aligns the public metadata with\nreality, and adds a one-line install note so users see the minimum\nbefore hitting an ESM error.\n\nFixes #1253\n\n* Update docs/docs/1-getting-started/2-installation/index.md\n\nCo-authored-by: Thomas Aribart <38014240+ThomasAribart@users.noreply.github.com>\n\n---------\n\nCo-authored-by: Thomas Aribart <38014240+ThomasAribart@users.noreply.github.com>",
        "url": "https://github.com/dynamodb-toolbox/dynamodb-toolbox/commit/792604815072e30d9835ac4fd42ac75f1ac55827"
    },
